products.name: Acer Predator Helios 300
products.description: The Helios 300 drops you right into the game with everything you need to obliterate the opposition on a blisteringly fast 240Hz1 /3ms2 display. Only now, we’ve armed it with an NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 30801, a 10th Gen Intel® Core™ i7 Mobile Processor1 and our custom-engineered 4th Gen AeroBlade™ 3D Technology.
